                    <span>I loved this book! Actually, I've read several of the Dummies books and liked them all; they really do put complex information in "plain English."  Retail Business Kit For Dummies is no exception.  After reading it I feel that I could run right out and open up a successful store! I'm not ready to quit my day job just yet. But someday . . . !</span>
                  
              
